{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21142.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"毬子亚弥华","nameRight":"保澄 雫","textRight":"之前……@你带我去看的那个……","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":101}],"textRight":"Needle Roller的……@“筋田”？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901}],"textLeft":"诶……@嗯……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":1}],"textRight":"听说筋田先生@私下是个很安静的人。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"诶诶！？@是、是吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"在舞台上明明……@总是很大声地吐槽别人……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"“想要改变腼腆的自己”……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"据说这就是他立志@成为搞笑艺人的原因。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"这样啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"他并不是你想象中的@那种开朗的人……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":401}],"textRight":"你会失望吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901}],"textLeft":"诶？@[chara:301901:motion_200:cheek_1:face_mtn_ex_030.exp.json]为、为什么这么问！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"我不会失望啊！@因为！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901}],"textLeft":"不管筋田@在舞台下是什么样子……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"我总能从筋田的表演中获得鼓舞，@这一点是真的……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"mouthOpen":1}],"textLeft":"啊……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"嗯，我也这么想。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":300}],"textRight":"无论何时何地……@无论在做什么……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"他就是他自己，@这一点是不会改变的。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"…………"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":101}],"textRight":"无论是筋田为了变得开朗@而站上舞台……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"还是亚弥华许愿让自己变得开朗@而成为魔法少女……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"都是凭借自己的决心重获新生的。@这是不会变的啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"…………"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"而且[chara:300701:lipSynch_0]……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"亚弥华你崇拜的朋友@叫什么名字？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901}],"textLeft":"诶？@大家叫她……优。"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story15","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":100}],"textRight":"我……还是第一次听说@她的名字。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"她的名字、声音……@还有笑起来的样子，我都不知道……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"用灿烂的笑容@鼓励我的人……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"并不是她……@更不是其他任何人……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":401}],"textRight":"毫无疑问……@就是亚弥华你啊。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"lipSynch":0}],"textLeft":"……！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901}],"textLeft":"唔……嗯[chara:301901:lipSynch_0]……@[chara:301901:motion_100:lipSynch_1]嗯！[chara:301901:tear_1]谢谢你！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"呵呵……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"没事的……没事的……@没事的……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901}],"textLeft":"现在的我……@[chara:301901:lipSynch_0][freeze:1][chara:301901:cheek_2:face_mtn_ex_010.exp.json][chara:301901:lipSynch_1]毫无疑问……[chara:301901:motion_0]也是真正的我……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"嗯……"},{"bg":"bg_adv_11042.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story02","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":100,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"textLeft":"好！@[chara:301901:cheek_1:face_mtn_ex_010.exp.json]感觉打起精神来了！","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"呵呵，那就好。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"雫！@谢谢你的鼓励！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701}],"textRight":"不客气。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"（毕竟你鼓励我的次数@要比这多得多嘛……）"},{"bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"对了！我要感谢你！@你收下它吧！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"诶？"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story09","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"Needle Roller的@演出门票……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"effect":"emotion_joy_0","face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}],"se":"7222_happy","textLeft":"我又@买到了两张！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300701,"lipSynch":0,"motion":401}],"textRight":"（诶！）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"为了提高中签率，@我特地抽了两张……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"不知道为什么，@余票好像还挺多的。"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301901}],"textLeft":"所以两张都被我买到了，@[chara:301901:cheek_0:face_mtn_ex_050.exp.json]真奇怪～为什么啊？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":300701,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"（呃……我倒是很明白@为什么有那么多余票……）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"那，@我们一起去看吧！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"诶……呃……@我……[chara:300701:cheek_0:face_mtn_ex_030.exp.json]还是不去了吧……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"诶！为什么啊？@[chara:301901:cheek_0:face_mtn_ex_050.exp.json]雫你……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"不是Needle Roller的@粉丝吗？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"effect":"emotion_surprise_0","face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":401}],"se":"7226_shock","textRight":"诶！？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"毕竟你@这么了解筋田！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":0}],"textRight":"啊……@那是因为……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"（他说的笑话@实在是太没意思了……）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp.json","id":300701,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"（所以我很想知道他@为什么要当艺人而已……）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":100}],"textLeft":"好不好嘛！[chara:301901:cheek_0:face_mtn_ex_010.exp.json]一起去吧！@[chara:301901:cheek_0:face_mtn_ex_011.exp.json]就这么定了！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300701,"motion":401}],"textRight":"诶，[chara:300701:cheek_0:face_mtn_ex_030.exp.json]等等！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":300}],"textLeft":"那个……@因为是５点开场……"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":300701,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"…………"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":300701,"lipSynch":0,"motion":200}],"textRight":"（嗯……算了……）"},{"autoTurnFirst":5.3,"bg":"bg_adv_narration.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3019_00_05","textHome":"嗯，你~好~！论开朗不输给任何人！@我是毬子亚弥华！"}],"nameCenter":"毬子亚弥华","textCenter":"嗨，你好～我是毬子亚弥华！@要论开朗，我可不会输给任何人哦！","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut","turnEffect":"stop"},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":301901,"motion":200}]},{"chara":[{"id":301901}]},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}